<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>dbt-colibri — not generated yet</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Hanken Grotesk", system-ui, sans-serif;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: #fafafa;
        color: #3a3a3a;
      }
      .box {
        max-width: 540px;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      code {
        background: #f0f0f0;
        padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: 0.85em;
      }
      h1 { color: #00a87a; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="box">
      <h1>Colibri dashboard not generated yet</h1>
      <p>
        This tab embeds the <strong>exact</strong> dbt-colibri dashboard (dbt-only, static).
        To populate it, run colibri on your dbt artifacts and drop the result here:
      </p>
      <p style="text-align: left">
        <code>pip install dbt-colibri</code><br /><br />
        <code>colibri generate --manifest manifest.json --catalog catalog.json</code><br /><br />
        then copy <code>dist/index.html</code> →
        <code>public/colibri/index.html</code> (replacing this file).
      </p>
      <p>
        Meanwhile, the <strong>Lineage Graph</strong> tab gives the full cross-tool
        (dbt&nbsp;↔&nbsp;PowerBI) column lineage built on your live API.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
